window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What's worse than fighting with allies? Fighting without them.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>Lily Singer - wizard and library archivist - has a problem. After finally learning the truth about her family's past, she finds she doesn't like it one bit. Now she must reconcile old grudges, make questionable allies, and bend the law to fix a problem that's not even her fault. Add to that having inconvenient feelings for her troublemaking witch friend while trying to date an overeager FBI agent, and Lily isn't sure she's strong enough to face the future, much less overcome it.&nbsp;</p> <p>With old friends and new allies making life complicated, Lily, Sebastian, and Sir Kipling must race to stop her father's evil plans before it's too late. Can they work together to save the day? Or will they let their differences divide them?</p>"; 
